{"tid":1792093,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:30:45.000Z","uid":311583,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd304c7e54b338e8e69387f021f6e65af4055f5","tid":1792093,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"你知道嗎？警察OT咗9.5億元，呢d都香港人交稅交出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近，政府凍結了星火同盟7000萬<br />\n<br />\n政府一直蠶食緊香港人嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你忍心嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我請你哋推呢個po，<br />\n懇請你哋喺時事台/政事台，開多個po,叫d人喺12月23日去稅局la<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=67a0ab24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3JuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=521f83eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"277788893a5a717a1582f8ecfb74878cd7a4db38","tid":1792093,"uid